item.title: SoftLayer_Software_License
item.description: SoftLayer_Software_License Datatype Description This class describes a specific type of license, like a Microsoft Windows Site License, a GPL license, or a license of another type. seeAlso SoftLayer_Software_Component SoftLayer_Software_Description Local id An ID number for this specific License type.
